metadata.name: Gnomes palabras #1
metadata.description: Gnomes palabras is a spell that takes you to the world of dwarves. hardworking dwarfs hide in caves, under sea rocks, they make mushroom circles of fairies, in the evenings they try on the outfits of snow white and the sorceress. the owls have already scattered apples for a spicy potion, one of which is poisoned. 'gnomes palabras' to shrink and find magical friends.
